{"type": "article", "id": 24000, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-17T07:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 25022, "name": "branding.ge"}, {"id": 25023, "name": "puzz'le design"}, {"id": 25024, "name": "David Ciernicki"}, {"id": 25025, "name": "Drew Cleaver"}, {"id": 636, "name": "伊东丰雄"}, {"id": 25026, "name": "AGNES SJÖBERG"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122622GOnN5rM4d1yvuzqi.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Major Tom by David Ciernicki</h2>\n<p>圆桌对于小空间来说往往是奢侈，这个木制圆桌则将桌腿和桌面分开。除此之外，设计师还在三根桌腿上增加了一个小的模块，可以像积木一样拼在上面以增加高度，适应不同大小的房间。设计者 David Ciernicki 来自德国，这是之前桌子的升级版，开发圆形木桌的灵活和实用。<a href=\"http://davidciernicki.com/2016/02/01/major-tom-2-0/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121010R0qxX6oBlMC8aTG2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121011H6mLINksh9Kci2Tl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121011o5Ok0ASWX3rpHlzd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121012MPVxJqNhZTYaKl12.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121012jbqw6I2e5QLV3tZh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Higher Hangers by Drew Cleaver</h2>\n<p>这款衣架想要为衣柜腾出更多的空间。设计师发现，传统的三角衣架使衣服和晾衣杆之间有很大空隙，通过改变衣架的形状，可以让衣服“调高”，以空出衣服下面真正有用的部分，就可以用来放鞋了。他制作了带天鹅绒表层和合成木两种，前者可以更好防滑，后者的使用时间更长。产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/higherhangers/higher-hangers-space-saving-closet-organization-re?utm_source=higherhangers.com&amp;utm_medium=l%3Cem%3E%3C/em%3Eink&amp;utm_co%3Cem%3E%3C/em%3Entent=higherhangers_l%3Cem%3E%3C/em%3Eink&amp;utm_campaign=kspledges\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021210137xWlHXCagDQM16ku.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121013dQvOGVxSiC9XsHNw.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021210141A9eX2KG8ESI0VkC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71764706\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121015ngyiXETh9RK2CjfU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.40220049\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121016UpG7kmzWE61M3LNe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46821516\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>mayuhana ma by 伊东丰雄&amp;yamagiwa</h2>\n<p>这款灯来自日本建筑师伊东丰雄，他在玻璃罩上用了黑色的丝线制作，横竖丝线在上面细密地铺开，在灯光的照射下可以看到明显的明暗差别，倒有点像素描画中的球体。尽管使用了轻盈的材料，却表现出了厚重感，可以应用在多个场合中。<a href=\"http://en.yamagiwa.co.jp/series/detail/1/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212101695Ucwr1MOR2DCGyF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63080685\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121017t0eR1uYX2EFTJCDW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121017sm0bKpj1GhCV2BTw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31295844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121018vojc0t5fB6bJsx7U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.97465146\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212101851J9qsNDyel4CGQd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>GRÖNT BY AGNES SJÖBERG</h2>\n<p>这是一套储藏蔬果的容器，它将蔬果展示出来同时提醒你该吃蔬菜了。设计师发现买回来的蔬菜常常遗忘在冰箱里或塑料口袋里，就设计了这组容器，分为三种方法保存，浸泡在水里，放在密闭的容器里和站在水里。你甚至还可以浇水，放在一起也组成一个装饰。<a href=\"http://analogueways.com/gront/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212101968a0jNEVhJtzR2KU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121019BrN8ifRyUZDmjO3a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121020iLtxv7hKRlkpHCSo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121020xPa8qhVFbSjo1U9W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021210215vq7wPnX1LibgrGV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>candle holder by puzz'le design</h2>\n<p>这几乎是最简单的烛台，它像一个微微上翘的纸片。它是铝制的，两头都带着可插蜡烛的圆孔。其中一头有些微的上扬和折痕，它套在下一个蜡烛上，围合成一个三角形或正方形，就像微微浮起的波纹，在简单和优雅中透着一些趣味。单个售价 35.62 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/wave-aluminium-pale-green-candle-holder/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121021uXO9nb2tAUK4oC8z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71382979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121022h3eyI5FqVsDiBd1n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71382979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121022xPYTjHlQ8wVvtuoA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71382979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121022JdDnMPNH2bteGiq7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71382979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121023Dfd1t3C54VyxXH8b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71382979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>RANINA by \"branding.ge\"</h2>\n<p>这款酒产自格鲁吉亚，它的名字 RANINA 源于当地的歌曲。包装上用近乎儿童画的笔调画出了一幅载歌载舞的风俗画，有拟人化的太阳和月亮，充满了弯曲的纹路和异域风情。背后的条纹码上也有小的图案，非常有趣，带着一些热闹和纯真。这一系列 5 种酒的图案是一样的，只在服饰和名字上面用了不同颜色的晕染，显示出不同的品种。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121023ISd3Olk8fFWjD9aq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121024nTHfLlPpQxUeRStC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121024fdt2KjLIMgYXkwy3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021210259AHJywtEhq1vluRN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}